e will have an online leaderboard, featuring worldwide rankings and rankings among your friends.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Over 15 vehicles</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Customize and upgrade your vehicles</strong><br></li><li><strong>More than 25 tracks and 5 maps</strong><br></li><li><strong>Boss racing challenges</strong><br></li><li><strong>Over 25 different synthwave songs</strong><br></li><li><strong>Different game modes</strong><br></li><li><strong>Online Leaderboards</strong><br></li><li><strong>Achievements</strong></li></ul>",
